"{\"uid\": \"fansided.com-posts-watch-noah-lyles-2024-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Noah Lyles is one of the biggest stars on Team USA but is still on the hunt for his first gold medal.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 101, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 42, \"end\": 50, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9369230427239563, \"rank\": 0.06732074346061756, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sprinter competes in the 100 meter, the 200 meter and will likely have a spot on the 4x100m relay team as well giving him three chances at gold at the2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 102, \"to\": 276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 261, \"end\": 275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles won bronze in the 200 meters at the 2021 Olympics after failing to qualify for the 100 meters.\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's won three World Championships in the 200 meter, another in the 100 meter and two more as a member of the 4x100 meter American relay team.\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7057097055236569, \"rank\": 0.4170075283618219, \"text\":